Span.Text: "If our store servers go down, a third of our business evaporates. It’s that simple. It’s absolutely critical that our store servers remain running, and with Hyper-V, we’ve reduced store downtime."
Lance Shinabarger, VP, Global Infrastructure, Domino’s Pizza
Domino’s Pizza Chain switched 10,000 store servers to Microsoft Hyper-V virtual servers to improve reliability and performance.
